Class Board

public final class Board
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

Classical 8x8 game board. Game board meant for 2 players (one playing whites and the other playing blacks). In each square, one or more counters of the same colour can be piled up.
